reviewText: This episode is based on Neelix's past.  Neelix's home planet was destroyed many years ago, because of a weapon created by Voyager's new alien visitor, Jetrel.  Jetrel wants Neelix (most likely last Talaxian  alive)to help with his experiment, but Jetrel has ulterior motives and lies  to everyone.  Neelix finds it nearly impossible to trust Jetrel with  anything, even if it means Neelix could die.
